:::The Destrocons:::

Skywarp: So when are we attacking the CF?
Dirge: yeah, i need some fighting, i haven;t been in a fight since, since-
Skywarp: Since Cerberus' guys came and tried to take over.
Dirge: Yikes! It has been LOOOOONG!
Ramjet: Calm down guys, we attack when Cygnar says we do.
Skywarp: yeah, well why's HE leader while Magmatron's gone? You were leader 
last time.
Ramjet: I am a warrior. I fight when i am needed.  Leaderrship would be nice, 
but Cygnar is a friend. Still, i would like to get started.
::he opens his comm::
Ramjet: Sorry if im interrupting anything important, but my team is getting 
restless.  When do we attack the Trainers?
